Actress Yetunde Bakare has advised guys on the best way to deal with an over-demanding girlfriend. Bakare also made sure to tip the generality of her fans on how to handle financial pressure from parents. According to her, an over-demanding girlfriend should be cut off from one’s life. “As a young guy, if your girlfriend is always demanding for things you cannot afford, chase her away,” she wrote.   Tiwa Savage demands 2022 Hilux, iPhone, others as birthday…     VIDEO: Actress MO Bimpe organises surprise birthday for…     Atiku’s daughter gifts Zubby Michael plot of land on…   - Advertisement - Advising against parents who assign financial responsibilities knowing fully well their ward is unemployed; she said such parents should be quizzed on where and how they expect the money for that need to be sourced from. She added: “As a child, if your parents are giving you responsibilities knowing fully well that you’re not working. Ask them how and where they expect you to get the money! “Don’t let anybody to pressurise you!”